      "tldr": "This release adds first-class PowerShell support on Windows. Plugin installs now preserve JSONC comments in configuration files, improving maintainability. The variant modal in the TUI has been improved to be less intrusive, and theme colors have been added for dialog textarea placeholders. A bug where `OPENCODE_DISABLE_CLAUDE_CODE_PROMPT` was not respected for project-level CLAUDE.md has been fixed. The patch tool has been renamed to apply_patch and its behavior clarified."
